Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IN ('-- Layouts: BI Publisher (XPT) layouts', 'Data Model Metadata', 'Report Metadata', 'Template File for Style Template or Sub Template') THEN '3 - Publisher Objects' WHEN "%1" IN ('List Export', 'Marketing BI Data Load', 'Marketing Saved ResultSet', 'Segment') THEN '7 - Marketing Segmentation' WHEN "%1" IN ('KPI', 'Scorecard Cause And Effect Linkages', 'Scorecard Causes And Effects View', 'Scorecard Custom Tree View', 'Scorecard Initiative', 'Scorecard Initiative Tree', 'Scorecard Objective', 'Scorecard Perspective', 'Scorecard Perspective List', 'Scorecard Settings', 'Scorecard Strategy Map View', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree View', 'Watchlist') THEN '5 - Scorecard Objects' WHEN "%1" IN ('Folder', 'Parameters: User ID, Password, Folder Path --', 'Shortcut') THEN '6 - Folders and Users' WHEN "%1" IN ('Action', 'Agent', 'Condition') THEN '4 - Actions, Agents & Conditions' WHEN "%1" IN ('Dashboard', 'Dashboard Page') THEN '1 - Dashboards' WHEN "%1" IN ('Analysis', 'Dashboard Prompt', 'Filter') THEN '2 - Analysis' ELSE 'Other' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('-- Layouts: BI Publisher (XPT) layouts', 'Data Model Metadata', 'Report Metadata', 'Template File for Style Template or Sub Template') THEN '3 - Publisher Objects' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('List Export', 'Marketing BI Data Load', 'Marketing Saved ResultSet', 'Segment') THEN '7 - Marketing Segmentation' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('KPI', 'Scorecard Cause And Effect Linkages', 'Scorecard Causes And Effects View', 'Scorecard Custom Tree View', 'Scorecard Initiative', 'Scorecard Initiative Tree', 'Scorecard Objective', 'Scorecard Perspective', 'Scorecard Perspective List', 'Scorecard Settings', 'Scorecard Strategy Map View', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree View', 'Watchlist') THEN '5 - Scorecard Objects' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('Folder', 'Parameters: User ID, Password, Folder Path --', 'Shortcut') THEN '6 - Folders and Users' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('Action', 'Agent', 'Condition') THEN '4 - Actions, Agents & Conditions' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('Dashboard', 'Dashboard Page') THEN '1 - Dashboards' WHEN "10 - Usage Tracking"."WS Objects Attributes"."Signature" IN ('Analysis', 'Dashboard Prompt', 'Filter') THEN '2 - Analysis' ELSE 'Other' END
